  "detailed_description": "Blood Red is an immersive co-op horror game that plunges players into a world<br>where ancient dark ritual stones have fallen from the sky, possessing an ominous power that<br>endangers innocent lives. As agents of P.A.R.M.A, the Paranormal Anomaly Research and<br>Metaphysical Agency, players must investigate the origin and nature of these malevolent<br>artifacts.<br><br>In this heart-pounding supernatural adventure, players will navigate through atmospheric<br>environments,craft ritual stones, and confront nightmarish demons in combat. With seamless<br>1-4 player co-op gameplay, teamwork and communication are crucial for survival.<br>Coordinate your efforts, combine your skills, and overcome terrifying challenges together.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Intense co-op horror experience for 1-4 players</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Detect the Demon Type!</strong><br>Use all the tools at your disposal to find out which demon you're facing.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/1b211d5254ecf6b49086100fd5eb8acd.poster.avif?t=1697814132\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/1b211d5254ecf6b49086100fd5eb8acd.webm?t=1697814132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/1b211d5254ecf6b49086100fd5eb8acd.mp4?t=1697814132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Fight For Your Survival!</strong><br>Use your melee or ranged weapon to fight foes that are called the \"Dark Companions.\"<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/544de6c86eecaf98b7da67ad67905ca8.poster.avif?t=1697814132\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/544de6c86eecaf98b7da67ad67905ca8.webm?t=1697814132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/544de6c86eecaf98b7da67ad67905ca8.mp4?t=1697814132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Craft Ritual Stones!</strong><br>Craft ritual stones using all the crafting parts you have gathered.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/81b4f52a3c878a0bc91462fe661c6053.poster.avif?t=1697814132\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/81b4f52a3c878a0bc91462fe661c6053.webm?t=1697814132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/81b4f52a3c878a0bc91462fe661c6053.mp4?t=1697814132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Blood Red is an immersive co-op horror game that plunges players into a world<br>where ancient dark ritual stones have fallen from the sky, possessing an ominous power that<br>endangers innocent lives. As agents of P.A.R.M.A, the Paranormal Anomaly Research and<br>Metaphysical Agency, players must investigate the origin and nature of these malevolent<br>artifacts.<br><br>In this heart-pounding supernatural adventure, players will navigate through atmospheric<br>environments,craft ritual stones, and confront nightmarish demons in combat. With seamless<br>1-4 player co-op gameplay, teamwork and communication are crucial for survival.<br>Coordinate your efforts, combine your skills, and overcome terrifying challenges together.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Intense co-op horror experience for 1-4 players</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Detect the Demon Type!</strong><br>Use all the tools at your disposal to find out which demon you're facing.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/1b211d5254ecf6b49086100fd5eb8acd.poster.avif?t=1697814132\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/1b211d5254ecf6b49086100fd5eb8acd.webm?t=1697814132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/1b211d5254ecf6b49086100fd5eb8acd.mp4?t=1697814132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Fight For Your Survival!</strong><br>Use your melee or ranged weapon to fight foes that are called the \"Dark Companions.\"<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/544de6c86eecaf98b7da67ad67905ca8.poster.avif?t=1697814132\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/544de6c86eecaf98b7da67ad67905ca8.webm?t=1697814132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/544de6c86eecaf98b7da67ad67905ca8.mp4?t=1697814132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Craft Ritual Stones!</strong><br>Craft ritual stones using all the crafting parts you have gathered.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/81b4f52a3c878a0bc91462fe661c6053.poster.avif?t=1697814132\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/81b4f52a3c878a0bc91462fe661c6053.webm?t=1697814132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194570/extras/81b4f52a3c878a0bc91462fe661c6053.mp4?t=1697814132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li></ul>",
